{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"120752","text":"Considering what's on television these days, it would be appropriate to only have those people pay who actually (want to) follow the programming.","type":"I","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120753","text":"In some cases there are only shows for older generations on at prime times, so why then should everyone pay for this?","type":"I","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120754","text":"By now you have advertising on all channels,","type":"I","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120755","text":"so there's no advantage for the current paying viewers of the public broadcasters.","type":"I","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120756","text":"Nevertheless one has to point out that there'd probably be way fewer stations if it weren\u2019t the whole of Germany that\u2019s obliged to pay.","type":"I","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120757","text":"That shouldn't be an issue though, given the sheer number of programmes and stations that essentially show the same things anyway.","type":"I","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120758","text":"Default Inference","type":"RA","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120759","text":"Default Inference","type":"RA","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120760","text":"Default Inference","type":"RA","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120761","text":"Default Conflict","type":"CA","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"},{"nodeID":"120762","text":"Default Conflict","type":"CA","timestamp":"2015-12-14 12:11:36"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"161644","fromID":"120753","toID":"120758","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161645","fromID":"120758","toID":"120752","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161646","fromID":"120754","toID":"120759","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161647","fromID":"120759","toID":"120755","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161648","fromID":"120755","toID":"120760","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161649","fromID":"120760","toID":"120752","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161650","fromID":"120756","toID":"120761","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161651","fromID":"120761","toID":"120752","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161652","fromID":"120757","toID":"120762","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"161653","fromID":"120762","toID":"120761","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[]}